snippet.title: Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek - Lyrical | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe üëâ https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek'' from the much-awaited film ''The Devil'' featuring Challenging Star Darshan. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. Tune in now and feel the vibe. 

Song Credits:
Song Name : Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer : Deepak Blue
Lyrics : Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer : Santhu Master
Additional Vocals : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Aniruddha Sastry & Group
Keyboard : B Ajaneesh Loknath, V Sukumar
Rhythm : Ricky D‚ÄôCosta, Kalyan Chakravarthy, Sukumar V, B Ajaneesh Loknath
Mixed & Mastered By : Sanjay Kumar M P, Renu Digi Studio, Bangalore
Music Production : C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios Bangalore

Movie Credits:
Starring : Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai, Mahesh Manjrekar, Achyuth Kumar, Sharmila Mandre.
Produced by: J Jayamma & Saregama
Directed by: Prakash Veer
Executive Producer : Thashwini Veer
Dialogue : Kanth Raj S S
Direction Department : Mohan Malagi, M S Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth, Sanjana Sudhakarr
Director Of Photography (DOP) : Sudhakarr S Raj
Music Director : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios
Editor : Harish Komme
Art Director : Mohan B Kere
Action Director : Ram Lakshman
Colourist : Ashwath
Post Production : Annapurna Studios
Managers : Suresh K Mysore, Jagadish Rao R.
Still Photography : Kadur Raghu & Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video : Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
He Breaks All Time Records

Pallavi:
Nammovrene Nange Bossu
Nanu Badkod For The Fansu
Khaasa Aadre Daasa Naanu
Dosti Nibhaaisu

First Day First Show Theatre Alli
Damaal Dimeel Soundinalli !!
Celebration Maadovr Nijvaad Celebritiesu

Hasividdare Saadhne Maadona
Kashta Padovrge Keerti Nidhaana
Namma Bhaashene Nange Pradhaana
Nera Nudile Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
Forever Record Breaks

Charanam 1:
Cut-Out Andre Naan Antaare
Daulat Ella‚Ä¶ No Chance

Yaariginta Naaven Kammi
Anta Aagu‚Ä¶ Advance

Ille Hutti Ille Beledu Niyattaagi Ille Duddu
Oorudhdhaara Maadovr Naavu Pakka Localsu!

Yeshte Saahukaara Idru Oorigoore Kondkondidru
Nanna Preetsovr Maatra Nange Celebritiesu

Yene Aagogli
Cho-Ninna Bidovr Naavalla

Nanna Mansalli
Cho-Hachcheyaagirteev Naavella

Beda Namage Berevr Kathe Puraana
Nera Nudile Matte Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

|| Rap Repeat ||

Charanam 2:
Oyy
Cho-Yenappa
Actually En Gotta Chinna
Cho-Helappa

Ninna Belavanige Ninna Kaiyyalle
Make Your Future Brightu!
Hit Aagodmele Nam Hudga Annovrge
Don‚Äôt Need To Be Sweetu!

Prathibhege Illi Kone Illa..
KaleLyoru Kammi Illa‚Ä¶

Nuggi Neevu Munde Bandu Nintre‚Ä¶
Nimge Yashassu

Akkapakkadavra Maatu Keli..
Addressgildang Aagogbedi‚Ä¶
Nimma Nambirovrigella
Neeve Taane The Bossu!!

Nimma Preetige Chiraruni Naa
Ella Nammovre Anta Baalona

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

|| Rap Repeat ||

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

snippet.title: Madharasi - Concept Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh | Sri Lakshmi Movies
snippet.description:
Madharasi - Concept Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh | Sri Lakshmi Movies

‚ùØ‚ùØ In this Concept trailer video I'm displaying visual commentary on how a film idea could look, The purpose of This Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos is to demonstrate and conceptualize specific or non-existing film ideas, compile and transform clips from previously existing productions to create a creatively unique vision and giving new meaning. I've transformed the original work by adding My own unique value such as added high-quality edits and special effects to create completely new, original movie trailers. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

‚ùØ‚ùØ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

localized.description:
Madharasi - Concept Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh | Sri Lakshmi Movies

‚ùØ‚ùØ In this Concept trailer video I'm displaying visual commentary on how a film idea could look, The purpose of This Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos is to demonstrate and conceptualize specific or non-existing film ideas, compile and transform clips from previously existing productions to create a creatively unique vision and giving new meaning. I've transformed the original work by adding My own unique value such as added high-quality edits and special effects to create completely new, original movie trailers. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

‚ùØ‚ùØ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

‚ùØ‚ùØ Subscribe Flix Series

      2021flixseries@gmail.com

snippet.description:
Punjabi Aa Gaye Oye is an upcoming Punjabi Movie starring Prince Kanwaljit Singh, Singga, and Twinkle Arora in lead roles. Directed by Aditya Sood, this emotionally charged drama promises action, heart, and entertainment, releasing worldwide on 5th September 2025.

Saiyaara (1980) - Kishore Kumar's Saiyaara Full Song
Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance,timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Whether you're a lifelong Kishore fan or discovering his magic for the first time, this song is a journey into the past that you don't want to miss..

Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Jo tujhko na paaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha

Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

snippet.title: #Video | Najariya Najar Se |Godfather | #Khesari Lal Yadav |#Priyanka Singh |New Bhojpuri Song 2025
snippet.description:
"Najariya Najar Se" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, the song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Najariya Najar Se" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, the song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

snippet.title: JALSA | Teaser | Mantra Muugdha | Suryamayee | Sanoj | Manmay Dey | Sarthak | Anupam Patnaik | TM
snippet.description:
Here‚Äôs the promo for the most awaited chartbuster of the year! 

Step into the ultimate dance revolution with ‚ÄúJalsa‚Äù ‚Äì a track built to ignite every floor, fuel every workout, and turn every moment into a celebration! With thunderous beats, electrifying grooves, and melodies that refuse to leave your head, this anthem is more than music ‚Äì it‚Äôs pure energy.


Feel the rush. Own the night. Keep the vibe alive.

Share the groove. Spread the love. This is Jalsa Night! 

Tarang Music is the official music label of Mantra Muugdha.

Song Credits - 

Music Composed & Produced by Ashish Pradhan
Singers : Humane Sagar, Antara Chakraborty 
Lyrics : Manoj Kumar Panda
